== OVERVIEW ==

For different parts of this project, different licenses apply. This is because some 3rd party 
components (mostly artwork such as, for example, fonts and icons) have been released under different 
licenses and, of course, these licenses continue to apply to those components and their authors 
retain all rights within the original licenses. All licenses are free(ish) / open source(ish) 
licenses but that doesn't imply they are compatible. In the following, we will distinguish between 
the core license which covers the contributions of this project and the 3rd party licenses which 
cover the 3rd party components used by this project.

IMPORTANT: All 3rd party components can be found in the ./resources folder and contain a copy of 
           their respective license. Not all contents of the ./resources folder are necessarily 3rd 
           party components. A complete list of 3rd party components and their licenses is given 
           below.  
           
IMPORTANT: The creators and copyright holders of 3rd party components are not affiliated with this 
           project, endorse it or can be held liable for any content from this project. Their sole 
           responsibility is for their original creations and for these just within the scope of  
           the respective licenses.

=== Core License ===  

This project (except 3rd party components) is distributed under the GNU General Public License 
(GPL) v3 license. A copy pf the GPL v3 can be found in the LICENSE_GPLv3 file or on 
<http://www.gnu.org/licenses/>.

